jokes.setup: Why do Java programmers hate communism?
jokes.punchline: They don't want to live in a classless society.

jokes.joke:
Judge: "I sentence you to the maximum punishment..."
Me (thinking): "Please be death, please be death..."
Judge: "Learn Java!"
Me: "Damn."
